1
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,440
You only have three minutes

2
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,440
to replace the real Lan Hewei.

3
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,440
Later, you find a chance to wake up

4
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,360
and lurk around Lin Mojiao

5
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,640
to finish the plan.

6
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,360
Before I met you,

7
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:43,320
my life was always in darkness.

8
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,560
At that time, you were like the sun,

9
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,400
warm

10
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,000
and dazzling.

11
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:51,920
You don't know

12
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,560
how important you are to me.

13
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,640
[I never thought someone like you]

14
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,920
[would fall in love with me without hesitation.]

15
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:06,480
[I know it's painful for you to become a vegetable.]

16
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,280
[So for me,]

17
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,200
[and for you,]

18
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:13,040
[just die quietly like this.]

19
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,920
[But Lin Mojiao]

20
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,400
[can't wait to kill me.]

21
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:18,360
President Lin,

22
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,560
Lanhe Group is waiting.

23
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:54,520
I'm not Lan Hewei.

24
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,520
I'm not trying to take your identity.

25
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,960
I never forgot...

26
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:22,640
Never.

27
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,480
I'm not Lan Hewei.

28
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,360
I'm Xu Meng.

29
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,760
Lan Hewei is my sister.

30
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,360
Vivi,

31
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,360
believe it or not,

32
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,240
I will get you out of there.

33
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:29,920
Lu Xing,
do you want to...

34
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:47,720
Get up.

35
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:48,920
What are you waiting for?

36
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:27,000
Can you hold on?

37
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,120
Your opponent is Lin Mojiao.

38
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:50,080
As his wife,

39
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,600
you have to be 100% committed to this role

40
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:55,360
to make him lower his guard.

41
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,320
I'm Lin Mojiao now.

42
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,600
Use what I taught you.

43
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:04,960
Relax.

44
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,480
Don't be afraid.

45
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:29,400
Touch me.

46
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:41,680
Not enough.

47
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:41,120
That's all you've learned?

48
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,400
That's it for today.

49
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,120
I've bought you a ticket back to China tomorrow.

50
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,360
I shouldn't have dragged you into this.

51
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,080
It's my fault.

52
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,840
If she knows your identity...

53
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:57,800
She will never know.

54
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:43,760
Sir.

55
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:44,960
Something's wrong.

56
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:49,480
Back to China.
